casebody.data:
Robin M. OWENS, Personal Representative of the Estate of Kenneth Gene Owens, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
MANTHA MANAGEMENT GROUP, INC., d/b/a Tim Horton's of Waterford, Defendant-Appellee,
and
Meco Property Maintenance, Inc., Leonard C. Carnaghi, Inc., Nagle Paving Company, THD Donut Delaware, Inc., and Tim Donuts US Limited, Inc., Defendants. SC: 158454
COA: 338392 Supreme Court of Michigan. June 5, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the June 28, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
